metadata.name: Talbot Road
metadata.description:
Pretty Mundane is my way of honouring an elegance in the pedestrian; saluting the little things in life that really do matter.

Pretty Mundane Volume One (2020) is a self-published, self-designed, self-sequenced and self-released zine, limited to 200 copies. 

These NFTs are 35 of the photographs from the sold out publication.
